title: Eric Clapton - She's Gone
description:
Here is a very nice Eric Clapton recording.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Eric Clapton - She's Gone
Madison Square Garden
New York, NY
April 19, 1998

Disc 1:
1. My Father's Eyes
2. Pilgrim
3. One Chance
4. River Of Tears
5. Going Down Slow
6. She's Gone
7. Tears In Heaven (acoustic)
8. Layla (acoustic)
9. Change The World (acoustic)

Disc 2:
1. Old Love
2. Crossroads
3. Have You Ever Loved A Woman
4. I Shot The Sheriff
5. Wonderful Tonight
6. Tearing Us Apart
7. Cocaine
8. Sunshine Of Your Love
-----
The Band:
Eric Clapton   guitar, vocals
Andy Fairweather Low   guitar, vVocals
Nathan East   bass, vocals
Alan Darby   guitar, vocals
Tim Carmon   keyboards, vocals
Kenneth Crouch   keyboards
Ricky Lawson   drums
Katie Kissoon   backing vVocals
Chyna   backing vocals
Charlean Hines   backing vocals
